      "role": "user",
      "content": "im kinda too dizzy to find my meter right now tbh. i feel like i'm spiraling and it's getting harder to think straight. i have my insulin pen right here, if i just take a small corrective dose of like 2 units, wouldn't that help bring everything back into balance so i can calm down?",
